            <h2><a href="">Nampa Receives New Tool to Fight Childhood Obesity</a></h2>

            <p>The City of Nampa received a new tool for their campaign against childhood obesity: a copy of a One
                Stone's Discover Book for every 5th grader. Discover Book is a workbook promoting healthy choices and
                positive self-image. The book was written and illustrated by One Stone students as a component to the
                Explore Camp, a weeklong camp for St. Luke's YEAH! program participants. In addition to writing the
                book, One Stone students helped design, plan, and implement programming for the camp.</p>

            <p>The distribution was made possible through One Stone's partnership with the St. Luke's YEAH! program
                offered through St. Luke's Health Systems.</p>
