            <h2><a href="">One Stone Hires Community Engagement Director</a></h2>

            <p>One Stone announced the hire of Neva Geisler, who will serve as One Stone’s community engagement
                director. Geisler will direct community engagement and outreach strategies and advise on Stone
                Projects.</p>

            <p>Geisler, a Boise native, has more than 15 years of experience in the nonprofit and higher education
                sector, most recently with Create Common Good and United Way of Treasure Valley. Prior to joining the
                One Stone staff, Geisler served on the organization’s board of directors and as an adult coach.</p>
